quote.summary: Top Education Group Ltd is an Australia-based private tertiary education provider. The Company trades as the Australian National Institute of Management and Commerce (IMC), as well as Top Education Institute. The Company is principally engaged in providing private higher education services and English language courses in Australia. With campuses located in cities across Australia, namely Sydney, Perth and Hobart, the Company offers tertiary education within the three core schools of business, law and information technology (IT). The Company provides a range of courses under the Self-Accrediting Authority, such as Bachelor of International Business, Master of Accounting Intelligence, Graduate Certificate in Business, Graduate Certificate in Data Analytics and others. Its Business School provides quality programs at both undergraduate and postgraduate levels. The relevant courses are also accredited by professional bodies, such as ACCA, CPA Australia and CAANZ.
